      "name": "Topics Broad Enough",
      "description": "",
      "instruction": "It's very important that these are broad enough; they should have a high likelyhood of including what the user wishes to say. Each should be general enough, and the set broad enough, that the set of 6 together covers almost all of the things the user may wish to continue with (replacing the sentence fragment in the case of Task 1, and the next sentence in the case of Task 2).\n\nEven when one topic seems much more likely, the rest should be other non-oerlapping topics.",
